modName: Thalmor Influence - Markarth's shrine of Talos lockdown
summary: Locks Markarth's Talos' Shrine door and places two Thalmor guards to guard it.
descriptionHtml:
As requested by Ravenlash (@NEXUS) I made another Thalmor Influence mod.

This mod locks the door of the shrine of Talos in Markarth and places two Thalmor guards by the door.
Both guards have a key to the shrine.

A couple of vanilla quests force open the door so don't get confused if it isn't locked.
for example,the Door Will Be Open During The Forsworn Conspiracy Quest.
author: gtantsa
